env.CALI_MPIREPORT_CONFIG: SELECT annotation, mpi.function, min(sum#sum#time.duration) as "exclusive_time_rank_min", max(sum#sum#time.duration) as "exclusive_time_rank_max", avg(sum#sum#time.duration) as "exclusive_time_rank_avg", min(inclusive#sum#time.duration) AS "inclusive_time_rank_min", max(inclusive#sum#time.duration) AS "inclusive_time_rank_max", avg(inclusive#sum#time.duration) AS "inclusive_time_rank_avg", percent_total(sum#sum#time.duration) AS "Exclusive time %", inclusive_percent_total(sum#sum#time.duration) AS "Inclusive time %" GROUP BY prop:nested FORMAT json
env.CALI_MPIREPORT_LOCAL_CONFIG: SELECT sum(sum#time.duration), inclusive_sum(sum#time.duration) GROUP BY prop:nested
